utes and have inheritance, without having for developers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to implement all tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme contract"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"final"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" class, its type cannot be seen as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sendable"},{"type":"text","text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSPinCodeInput":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"PIN code input is a UI element that allows to capture short, fixed-length numeric codes, typically for authentication or confirmation purposes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as a four, six or eight-digit personal identification number (PIN)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PIN code input is presented as a series of individual input fields or boxes, each representing a single digit, to enhance readability and encourage accurate input,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while supporting smooth keyboard navigation and secured input masking if needed."}],"title":"OUDSPinCodeInput","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudspincodeinput","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSPinCodeInput","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSPinCodeInput"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSPinCodeInput"}]}}}